<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    No reviewed suppressions are needed here. The module's types are written to keep SpotBugs quiet on
    their own merits: money is held as integer cents (no floating-point currency), LineItem is an
    immutable validating record, and Cart takes a defensive copy of its lines, so the representation-
    exposure detectors stay quiet without a filter entry. The file is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely
    reviewed false positive has a home — named narrowly by class, method, and pattern, with a reason —
    rather than being suppressed inline or by disabling a detector wholesale (Chapter 16 / Chapter 19).
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
